# Input

```graphql
query DemoQuery {
	user(
		# biome-ignore format: preserve the nested argument formatting
		filter: { id: $id,  active: true } # keep this trailing comment after the suppressed argument
		status: ACTIVE
	) {
		id
	}
}

```


# Formatted

```graphql
query DemoQuery {
	user(
		# biome-ignore format: preserve the nested argument formatting
		filter: { id: $id,  active: true } # keep this trailing comment after the suppressed argument
		status: ACTIVE
	) {
		id
	}
}

```

